45:20.400 --> 45:21.400
users.

45:21.400 --> 45:25.020
So yes, it does share a common heritage with Red Hat Enterprise Linux.

45:25.020 --> 45:27.080
It's similar to CentOS.

45:27.080 --> 45:33.160
