46:04.440 --> 46:10.640
So UBI, I saw a lot of the development that went on around UBI when I was still at Red

46:10.640 --> 46:11.640
Hat.

46:11.640 --> 46:13.520
UBI is interesting.

46:13.520 --> 46:16.120
